《惊魂记》最后成为了我最重要的成就之一

997
01:29:55,851 --> 01:30:01,099
and Alma and I got to keep the house and the swimming pool.
我们俩的房子和游泳池最后也没卖掉

998
01:30:01,122 --> 01:30:04,445
But you know what they say in Hollywood:
不过你也知道Hollywood的规矩：

999
01:30:04,469 --> 01:30:08,011
You're only as good as your last picture.
最后一部电影论成败

1000
01:30:08,029 --> 01:30:12,573
So if you'll excuse me, I had better toddle away
所以抱歉各位，我还是回去

1001
01:30:12,597 --> 01:30:17,373
to begin the exhaustive search for my next project.
开始展开下一个计划的奔波

1002
01:30:17,397 --> 01:30:24,913
Unfortunately, I find myself once again quite bereft of any inspiration.
不幸的是，我再一次没灵感了

1003
01:30:24,937 --> 01:30:30,778
However, I do hope something comes along soon.
然而，我还是希望有点小东西能快点出现

1004
01:30:35,548 --> 01:30:37,984
Good evening.
黑夜到了

